## GUIDES
- [Min Difficulty and Max Difficulty table for missions](https://www.speedrun.com/Helldivers2/guides/y5pu3).
- How to downpatch your game [manually](https://www.speedrun.com/Helldivers2/guides/zf9n8) or [with a version manager](https://www.speedrun.com/Helldivers2/guides/e9976).
- [How to play Meridia/Gloom missions](https://www.speedrun.com/Helldivers2/guides/ep9oo).
_____

## 1.000.300
**Release**: April 29th 2024.
- First playable downpatch.
- Eruptor has its original shrapnel but nerfed magazine (**not currently usable on downpatch**).
- Meridia missions added.
_____

## 1.000.305
**Release**: June 1st 2024.
- Infinite Grenade glitch.
- Last patch for the original Meridia missions event.
- Last patch where Retrieve Essential Personnel is playable.
- Stratagem replacement exploit to equip both Patriot and Emancipator Exosuits.
_____

## 1.000.400
**Release**: June 13th 2024.
- Fix of the Infinite Grenade glitch.
- Removal of the AA-Defenses operation modifier (reduces the stratagem slots by 1).
- Removal of the Retrieve Essential mission.
_____

## 1.000.405
**Release**: July 10th 2024.
- Last patch before Escalation of Freedom.
_____

## 1.001.002
**Release**: August 6th 2024.
- Escalation of Freedom release.
- 10 | SUPER HELLDIVE added.
- Enemy Bio-Processors and Retrieve Mutant Larva optional objectives added.
- Impalers, Barrager Tank, Reinforced Scout Strider and Spore Charger added.
- Poor Intel operation modifier (hides the exact location of Missions Objectives) added.
- Removal of the Atmospheric Interference operation modifier (reduces the accuracy of all Orbital stratagems).
_____

## 1.001.005
**Release**: August 21th 2024.
- Last patch with the pre-nerfed Commando.
_____

## 1.001.100
**Release**: September 17th 2024.
- Commando nerf (now unable to one-shot fabricators).
- Emergency Evacuation skip.
- Invincible Shield Pack glitch.
_____

## 1.001.101
**Release**: September 18th 2024.
- Fix of the Invincible Shield Pack glitch.
- Start of the 60 days timeline.
_____

## 1.001.104
**Release**: October 15th 2024.
- End of the 60 day timeline.
- Last patch where the Meridia missions are playable.
- Supply fills visible on the minimap.
_____

## 1.001.201
**Release**: October 19th 2024.
- Upload Escape Pod Data mission moved from 2 | EASY · 3 | MEDIUM to 1 | TRIVIAL · 2 | EASY.
_____

## 1.002.001
**Release**: December 13th 2024.
- Omens of Tyranny release.
- Ability to aim and stim whilst airborne using the Jump Pack.
- Expert Extraction Pilot enhanced by 100%.
- Muscle Enhancement enhanced by 40%.
- Peak Physique melee damage enhanced by 100%.
_____

## 1.002.101
**Release**: February 2nd 2025.
- Servants of Freedom release.
- Ability to jog while carrying barrels/SEAF Artillery Rounds.
- Emotes no longer negate fall damage.
- Pre-nerfed Ultimatum (extra ammo from Siege Ready and Hellpod Space Optimization, **currently not working on downpatch**).
_____

## 1.002.103
**Release**: February 11th 2025.
- Ultimatum extra ammo nerf.
_____

## 1.002.200
**Release**: March 18th 2025.
- Draw! emote release.
_____

## 1.002.203
**Release**: April 4th 2025.
- Last patch before Heart of Democracy.
- Last patch with pre-buffed bulk fabricators.
- Last patch with the old Galactic Map UI.
- Last patch with the pre-nerfed Ultimatum.
- Pacifist skip.
_____

## 1.003.000
**Release**: May 13th 2025.
- Heart of Democracy release.
- First patch with Speedy Pelican (lastly effective on **1.003.105**).
- Flag of Super Earth planting to carry packages/shells glitch.
- Illuminate Megacities added.
- Pre-nerfed Repel Invasion Fleet mission added.
- Stingray, Crescent Overseer and Fleshmob added.
- Stratagem Duping glitch.
- Stratagem Duplication with Weapon Customization glitch.
- Take Down Overship missions added.
- Ultimatum nerf (damage and demo force).
- Ultimatum extra ammo from Hellpod Space Optimization added.
- Weapon Customization added.
_____

## 1.003.001
**Release**: May 16th 2025.
- Fix of the Stratagem Duping glitch.
_____

## 1.003.003
**Release**: May 27th 2025.
- Fix of the Pacifist skip.
_____

## 1.003.101
**Release**: June 10th 2025.
- Ability to die faster in endless holes found in Terminid Megacities.
- Ability to stim mid-dive.
- First patch with the Megacity skip (fixed on **1.004.000**).
- Inability to reload in the FRV from a passenger seat (fixed on **1.004.100**).
- Pre-buffed Infested Towers health (Cleanse Infested District).
- Terminid Megacities added.
_____

## 1.003.103
**Release**: June 17th 2025.
- Infested Towers health (Cleanse Infested District) buffed from 2500 to 15000.
_____

## 1.003.200
**Release**: July 15th 2025.
- Automaton Megacities added.
- Broken Orbital Laser (spawns away from the stratagem ball beacon).
- Increased chest injury bleed damage from 1 to 10.
- Removal of Speedy Pelican.
- Significant drop of performances until patch **1.004.100**.
- Sabotage Supply Bases added at 10 | SUPER HELLDIVE (only in Megacities).
- War Striders added.
_____

## 1.004.000
**Release**: September 2nd 2025.
- Into the Unjust release.
- Hive World biome, enemies and missions added.
- Infinite Supply Pack fills glitch.
- Patch of the Megacity skip.
_____

## 1.004.100
**Release**: October 23th 2025.
- Automatons require visual confirmation before popping a flare.
- Better performances.
- Broken operation seeds generation.
- Changed Leviathans shooting-based weaponry to beam-based weaponry.
- Decreased health of Fleshmobs and Overseers.
- Fixed Fleshmobs hitbox.
- Fixed Rupture Strain.
- Fortress/Mega Nest in Automaton/Terminid Megacities added.
- Regained ability to reload in the FRV from a passenger seat.
- Second Air Base Tower to Sabotage Air Base added at 9 | HELLDIVE · 10 | SUPER HELLDIVE (outside of Megacities).
- Weak spots added to War Striders.
_____

## 1.005.000
**Release**: December 2nd 2025.
- Addition of Factory World missions.
- Ability to reload in the FRV from a passenger seat lost again.
- Chargers no longer speed up when exiting charge.
- Fix of the Infinite Supply Pack fills glitch.
- Inability to peep into bunkers by diving while in first person view.
- Medium-armored weak spot to the vents on the backside of the Bunker, AA, and Mortar emplacements added.
- Removal of Fortress/Mega Nest in Automaton/Terminid Megacities.
- War Striders now detonate mines.
